    "We use the design only to check the syntax and semantics of the generated assertions.",
    "No other refinement of assertions is done using the design.",
    "In this process, a correctly generated assertion can fix a bug (if any) in a design as well.",
    "CASE STUDY: RV TIMER The unstructured design specification of RV Timer is initially transformed to structured JSON format and presented as input to the LLM to generate the SVA.",
    "The LLM initially generated ten functional assertions."
